'''伯克郡郡旗'''是[[英格兰|英格兰]][[伯克郡|伯克郡]]的旗幟，並於2017年3月正式在{{tsl|en|Flag Institute|旗幟學會}}注冊為郡旗<ref name="FI-release">{{cite web|url=https://www.flaginstitute.org/wp/2017/05/berkshire-now-registry/|author=Flag Institute|title=Berkshire Now in the Registry|accessdate=4 June 2017|archive-date=2020-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200922234318/https://www.flaginstitute.org/wp/2017/05/berkshire-now-registry/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。郡旗從數款提議中選出<ref name="FI-register">{{cite web|url=https://www.flaginstitute.org/wp/flags/berkshire/|author=Flag Institute|title=Berkshire|accessdate=4 June 2017|archive-date=2019-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191113074337/https://www.flaginstitute.org/wp/flags/berkshire|dead-url=no}}</ref>，注冊前曾使用{{tsl|en|Berkshire County Council|伯克郡議會}}的旗幟暫代。

